snippet.title: BABIES & KIDS being CLUMSY and SLEEPY - Extremely FUNNY and CUTE!
snippet.description:
Being clumsy doesn't mean a bad thing, it can come out as a really funny and cute situation and these babies are proving it. What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
